title: + Major overhaul of the CompareCategoriesActivity
message:
+ Major overhaul of the CompareCategoriesActivity
+ Added easy methods for adding new indicators
+ CompareCategories now gets all data from ListOfIndicators.
+ Added on-demand loading of indicators when clicking on the group
parent.
+ Added data manipulation methods into Country to allow for adding of
indicator results. (No results fetched because clicking on child does
nothing).
+ Added "UnloadedIndicatorDescription"
* Edited image scaling in About Activity
- Removed indicator caching. The time taken to load the indicator is
extremely low, even on 3G.
